data.description: Highly desired Ropes ISD, just under 5 acres of unrestricted land!  This property has everything you need ~ 2 bedroom, 1 bath main home w/ large primary bedroom & walk-in closet ~ stainless steel appliances ~ fenced backyard ~ 30X40 insulated barn w/ office space ~ New well ~ Horse pens W/ pipe fencing ~ Over 3500 sq ft. partially completed barndominium, huge covered porch on South & East side, plumbing has been stubbed!
